{"id":"aed5be33dec4030972d04b2c6c36319e3057fa4c","url":"https://aimaketattoo.com/ai-tattoo-generator","title":"AI Tattoo Generator | Create Custom Tattoo Design Ideas","site_name":"Buzzing","source":"aimaketattoo.com","byline":null,"excerpt":"Turn text prompts into custom tattoo design concept images. Explore styles, placements, and tattoo design directions before refining your idea.","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><DIV><div><p>Who it helps</p><h2>Who Can Use This AI Tattoo Generator?</h2><p>Use AIMakeTattoo to turn rough tattoo ideas into tattoo design directions, whether you are planning your own tattoo, building design boards, or preparing for a studio conversation.</p></div><div><p>How it works</p><h2>How the AI Tattoo Generator Works</h2><p>Turn a rough idea into a tattoo design concept, compare directions, and refine the concept before moving forward.</p></div><div><div><p>Popular tattoo ideas</p><h2>Popular Tattoo Ideas to Generate</h2><p>Explore common tattoo idea directions you can describe in the generator, then choose style, placement, and detail level around that idea.</p></div><div><div><p><img alt=\"Black and grey lion head tattoo design with flowing mane and ornamental leaves\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 31vw, (min-width: 640px) 45vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-animal-lion-tattoos.webp&w=256&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-animal-lion-tattoos.webp&w=384&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-animal-lion-tattoos.webp&w=640&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-animal-lion-tattoos.webp&w=750&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-animal-lion-tattoos.webp&w=828&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-animal-lion-tattoos.webp&w=