bq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-dragon-western-tattoos.webp&w=3840&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-dragon-western-tattoos.webp&w=3840&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF\"></p><h3>龙纹身</h3><p>探索具有强烈轮廓和流动性的西方龙、黑工、哥特式或奇幻风格的龙方向。</p></div><div><p><img alt=\"Coiled snake tattoo design with black and grey shading and ornamental frame\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 31vw, (min-width: 640px) 45vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=256&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=384&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=640&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=750&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=828&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=1080&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=1200&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=1920&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=2048&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=3840&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-snake-ornamental-tattoos.webp&w=3840&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF\"></p><h3>蛇纹身</h3><p>通过大胆的对比和动作探索盘绕的蛇、蛇、装饰蛇、匕首蛇或花蛇的方向。</p></div><div><p><img alt=\"Black and grey memorial tattoo design with candle, rose, portrait silhouette, and ribbon shapes\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 31vw, (min-width: 640px) 45vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=256&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=384&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=640&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=750&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=828&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=1080&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=1200&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=1920&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=2048&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=3840&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-memorial-candle-rose-tattoos.webp&w=3840&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF\"></p><h3>纪念纹身</h3><p>在肖像、蜡烛、玫瑰、丝带、符号或个人细节周围塑造尊重的纪念纹身方向。</p></div><div><p><img alt=\"Compass, wave, and sun symbolic tattoo design in fine black and grey linework\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 31vw, (min-width: 640px) 45vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-symbolic-compass-wave-tattoos.webp&w=256&q=75&dpl=dpl_CWCGLbq1K5ooqtAZykiAcj6pYCmF 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Ftattoo%2Fidea-symbolic-com